                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18241028-79-off420 t18241028-79-cd421"></join>, a coat, value 2 l.; a waistcoat, value 5 s.; a pair of trowsers, value 5 s.; a shirt, value 5 s.; two neckcloths, value 2 s.; a pair of boots, value 10 s.; a pair of stockings, value 1 s., and a handkerchief, value 2 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18241028-79-victim750" type="victimName">
